  <brief_title>Evaluation of CLP With and Without Spironolactone in Heart Failure Patients With Chronic Kidney Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 1, Open-label, Randomized, Crossover Study to Assess the Safety, Tolerability, and Efficacy of CLP With and Without Spironolactone in Adults With Heart Failure</official_title>
  <sponsors>
